<p type="title">Law and order</p>
<p><em type="italic">The Ministry of Justice and the Police </em>shall: </p>
<list><p type="listitem">reduce and prevent crime</p>
<p type="listitem">improve civil protection and emergency planning</p>
<p type="listitem">contribute to expedient legislation that is adapted to societal developments</p>
<p type="listitem">safeguard the due process of law and right to a fair trial</p>
<p type="listitem">implement punishment whose goal is to return offenders to a normal life in community</p>
<p type="listitem">prevent and resolve conflicts</p>
</list><p>On this page you will find general information and documents relating to law and order. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p>
